    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Heap structure that allows fast access and updates.</para>
<para>Supports both max-heap operations (via the underlying <ref refid="structfaiss_1_1CMax" kindref="compound">CMax</ref> heap) and efficient min extraction via linear scan (with optional SIMD acceleration). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
